00:15:28.720 --> 00:15:30.540
No, I'm not.

00:15:30.540 --> 00:15:33.320
I'm just looking out for my staff, that's all.

00:15:33.320 --> 00:15:35.100
Ping isn't from here.

00:15:35.100 --> 00:15:38.540
If he's going out somewhere,
shouldn't I check up on him?

00:15:39.880 --> 00:15:44.880
