00:19:32.200 --> 00:19:36.670
You know, when you act like this,
it makes me fall for you even harder.

00:19:36.670 --> 00:19:38.720
I never said you couldn't.

00:19:47.930 --> 00:19:50.390
Uh... Sorry to interrupt.

00:19:50.390 --> 00:19:52.890
Maybe I should come back later.

00:19:52.890 --> 00:19:55.290
Wait, Yu.

00:19:55.290 --> 00:19:58.410
Did you need something? You're here early.

00:20:03.550 --> 00:20:05.410
Go on ahead to the bar first, okay?

00:20:05.410 --> 00:20:06.910
Okay.

00:20:13.300 --> 00:20:17.020
I wanted to consult with you about something.

00:20:17.020 --> 00:20:21.160
Than called me last night.
He told me everything about you two.

00:20:22.250 --> 00:20:25.550
I've been thinking about this for a while.

00:20:25.550 --> 00:20:30.040
I've decided I'm going to resign
from the company.

00:20:30.040 --> 00:20:34.540
If I quit, I won't have to see Than anymore.

00:20:34.540 --> 00:20:36.910
If that's really what you've decided,

00:20:36.910 --> 00:20:39.680
then I respect your decision.

00:20:39.680 --> 00:20:42.660
But I still want you to think it over
one more time.

00:20:42.660 --> 00:20:46.950
If I really go through with this,
will you be angry with me, Phu?

00:20:51.820 --> 00:20:54.400
The three of us grew up together.

00:20:55.500 --> 00:20:58.520
You're like a brother to me.

00:20:58.520 --> 00:21:01.600
Of course, I wouldn't be angry
over something like this.

00:21:01.600 --> 00:21:05.240
I just want you to be happy
with whatever you choose.

00:21:08.720 --> 00:21:11.380
I understand both of you.

00:21:11.380 --> 00:21:14.070
Than's feelings for you,

00:21:14.070 --> 00:21:17.980
and your perspective on the situation.

00:21:17.980 --> 00:21:21.220
